ISLAMABAD, Dec 25 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting  Farrukh Habib said on Saturday that life of Quaid-e-Azam Muhammad Ali Jinnah was a beautiful combination of courage, hard work, honesty, determination and truth.
In a tweet, the minister said the life of the Quaid-e-Azam was a beacon of light for young generation for making Pakistan a state as envisioned by the Quaid-e-Azam.
